		<longdescription>
		Compton is a compositor for X, and a fork of xcompmgr-dana.

		This branch includes a new blur method: The multi-pass dual kawase blur! Use it with the --blur-method kawase and --blur-strength LEVEL options. Only works with the glx backend!
		</longdescription>
		<use>
			<flag name="drm">Enable for drm support</flag>
			<flag name="dbus">Enable for dbus support</flag>
			<flag name="opengl">Enable for glx support</flag>
			<flag name="pcre">Enable for pcre support</flag>
			<flag name="xinerama">Enable for xinerama support</flag>
		</use>
